Base Name : Hellspace
Subtitle  : Bloodburst
Full Name : HELLSPACE: Bloodburst

Core Theme:
- Life is dead
- Blood is fuel
- Hell is space

World Setting:
Year 6643.

Humanity is extinct.
Only machines and demons remain.

Hell has spread into space.
Blood is the only energy left.

You are a machine powered by blood.
Something inside you is still human.

This is Hell.
This is its space.....

Core Gameplay:
1. Fast-paced arcade space combat
   - Inspired by ULTRAKILL (speed, aggression)
   - Dogfighting + high mobility

2. Two modes:
   - Ship mode (dogfighting, shooting)
   - Eject mode (dash + katana + parry)

Core Loop:
- Move fast
- Fight enemies
- Kill → gain blood
- Use blood to survive and stay aggressive

Core Mechanics:
- Boost (high speed movement)
- Dash (quick reposition)
- Parry (reflect projectiles)
- Blood pickup (resource gain)

Blood System:
- Enemies drop blood on death
- Blood restores health / fuel
- Aggression is required to survive

Enemies:
- Demonic / organic ships
- Aggressive behavior (push player)
- Designed to force movement

Performance Targets:
- 60 FPS on iGPU (minimum)
- 100+ FPS on mid-range GPU
- Low poly, minimal shaders
